Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.22,0:00:14.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要着陆了  你们注意不要被甩下去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.10,0:00:16.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,被甩下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.57,0:00:32.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯今天的着陆还勉勉强强过得去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.95,0:00:33.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这也算过得去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.20,0:00:36.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,惊险方能让冒险家成长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.66,0:00:38.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这话谁说的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:39.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.41,0:00:42.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,至理名言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.21,0:00:49.75,geci,,0,0,0,,在这流失了爱的城市中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.96,0:00:54.68,geci,,0,0,0,,那正在微笑的你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.38,0:01:05.27,geci,,0,0,0,,用足以扼杀孤独的力量  紧紧拥抱我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.94,0:01:13.57,geci,,0,0,0,,被束缚的Limit  解放它回归本始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.61,0:01:15.65,geci,,0,0,0,,纵燃燃殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:25.96,geci,,0,0,0,,也要在这渲染了艳丽的夜之尽头翩然起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.04,0:01:29.83,geci,,0,0,0,,就让它烙印于灵魂之上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.92,0:01:39.60,geci,,0,0,0,,来吧  尽情闪耀吧  眼前的你  昳丽无双
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:46.44,geci,,0,0,0,,在这夜之尽头  翩然起舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.48,0:01:50.48,geci,,0,0,0,,就让它烙印于灵魂之上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:58.40,geci,,0,0,0,,来吧  尽情闪耀吧  眼前的你  昳丽无双
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.16,0:02:01.78,geci,,0,0,0,,飞扬而上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.03,0:02:07.08,geci,,0,0,0,,在这流失了爱的城市中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:33.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬  再不走就抛下你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:45.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.21,0:02:47.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是  藏身之处之一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:52.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是其中最难以被发现的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.34,0:02:53.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是个洞窟而已吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:08.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这地面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:13.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢   我们要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:16.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:25.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:27.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,欸  就是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.21,0:03:30.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,欸  挺不错的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:33.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,刚站在入口的时候我还只有满心绝望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.39,0:03:41.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么  睡袋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:43.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,欸  睡袋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.56,0:03:45.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那个  就是类似于被子的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:47.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  就是那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:51.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  法拉利昂  那样用力扯的话  会扯破的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:03.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,从德尔扎因陛下那儿得到的东西啊你也随身带着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:09.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:20.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那么为什么身为这个国家的王子的你会被关进牢里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:25.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子  是叫做瞬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:28.56,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪儿遇到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:35.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,被关在牢里面的时候  他突然就出现在我面前了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:39.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了一个像光球一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:40.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:46.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  映在那里的却是我从来没见过的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:57.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙突然就从那里飞出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:03.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那团光里面映出的就是地上世界的景象吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:05.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:10.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:16.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:17.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,欸  不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:20.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你对那种东西感兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:23.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一般般吧  因为我的母亲是考古学家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:24.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,考古学家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:27.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一门调查关于世界历史的学问
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:33.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈看到这个的话  一定会非常高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:37.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,地球空洞说之类的  虽然有所耳闻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:39.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但没想到它是真实存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:42.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,记得好像是叫做理想乡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:46.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道  这里叫ENDORA啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.72,0:05:49.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  地上的人们不知道ENDORA吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:51.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:55.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但我想大家要是知道了的话一定会非常吃惊的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:58.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,地上人们要是知道了ENDORA之后会怎么想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:06:01.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是会开心地感叹“大发现！ ”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:03.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？我想应该是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:06.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是艾丽西亚知道了地上的存在之后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:08.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,难道从没有想过要去看一看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:10.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？没有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:15.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,ENDORA和地上这两个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:19.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可以相互承认对方的存在却决不能相互干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:24.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,据古代文献记载尤其是对于ENDORA来说没有任何利益
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.93,0:06:28.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,把地底说成是冥界地狱等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:32.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,通过散布种种传说  让地上的人们远离ENDORA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:34.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这其中应该是有所原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:36.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是另一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:39.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真正来到ENDORA的地上人里面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:43.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也有人传言地底存柱着名为理想乡的乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:46.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那是十多年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:48.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,古代遗迹巴别里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:53.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,被命名为巴别塔  用于连接地上和ENDORA的装置突然复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:55.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不久之后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:58.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,装置又停止了运转
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:06.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因此德尔扎因陛下命令王立研究所  再次开通巴别塔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:08.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但我却…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:09.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,反对这么做   是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.06,0:07:14.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这和帕斯卡尔离开城堡有关系的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:16.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:19.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才也说过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:22.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这里和地上不可相互干涉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:24.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:26.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:30.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉…这不像是研究者会说的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.37,0:07:32.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想要将研究引向成功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:35.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要让自己的感觉敏锐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.21,0:07:38.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,理论也是有极限的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.21,0:07:40.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.09,0:07:45.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,小少爷你年纪还小是不会懂的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:46.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:52.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来那家伙也无法接受与自己不合的意见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:55.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然称陛下为“那家伙"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:57.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而且他还是你的父亲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:57.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:01.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是他养育你长大吧那么他就是你父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:05.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是因为父子吵架被关进了地牢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.57,0:08:07.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:10.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道城堡里会派追兵过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:14.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让巴别塔不会这么简单就被重启
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:16.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我在设计图里动了一点点手脚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:19.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这些小伎俩我想也是时候被看破了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:22.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,研究所里有优秀的人才加入了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:25.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:26.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说陛下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.21,0:08:28.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为了开通巴别塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.97,0:08:29.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他会去巴比伦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:31.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.68,0:08:35.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可能的话我希望我们能够在德尔扎因王之前  先行前往巴比伦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:41.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让瞬返回其原先所处世界后我打算破坏巴别
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:46.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你愿意的话  就告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:46.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:51.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你被关进地牢的理由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:56.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:08:58.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,剑我会给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:00.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  帕斯卡尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:03.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你不恨夺走你研究成果的那家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.13,0:09:05.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么怨恨的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:06.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,研究在哪都能进行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:10.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至可以说我现在能够随心所欲快乐得很
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:16.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不能连累他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:23.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:24.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:32.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下  那种游戏…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:36.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不许对我提意见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:38.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:45.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,完全就像是变了一个人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:48.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,必须阻止殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:55.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么做  人偶不是太可怜了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.52,0:10:00.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:03.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安  殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:05.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:10.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.49,0:10:13.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉我来迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:16.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我是隶属王立研究所的研究员
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.87,0:10:20.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,今曰起将兼任教育殿下的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.79,0:10:22.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫帕斯卡尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:26.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我虽然对于剑术没什么自信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.83,0:10:29.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但有着各种有趣的秘笈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:33.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下愿意的话  我会把它们传授给殿下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.68,0:10:36.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一起愉快地学习吧  殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.43,0:11:20.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:23.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:27.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下请听我一言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:29.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:34.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,巴别塔再次开通的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:36.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,势必将会给ENDORA带来危机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:37.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:39.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么会这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:41.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是作为研究者的直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:43.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不应该是研究者说出来的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:45.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:47.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没听见朕的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:49.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不服从朕的做法的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:52.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那就不需要你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:54.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请留步陛下！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:55.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你被放逐了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:56.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,陛下！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:04.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙  总是抢走我重要的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:23.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就像是预料到我们会来似的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.83,0:12:26.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样啊帕斯卡尔这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:27.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:33.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,第二  第三  小队已经相继派往进行搜索了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:34.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:35.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:38.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的任务已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:42.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,即是说接下来的事都交给我们处理就行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:42.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.47,0:12:45.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是王的命令退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:53.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  一开始就让我们去帕斯卡尔那里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:56.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就不用浪费这么多时间了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:58.36,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,未必如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.28,0:13:03.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,首先去打探一下   绝不允许杀害任何一人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:04.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.37,0:13:07.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都给我记在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:08.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:09.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,同意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:10.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,啊唔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:14.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,应该会在这住上一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:16.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我得去趟山下的小镇买点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:18.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,老老实实等我回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:24.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我也是通缉犯对啦  所以这是以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:26.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  应该行得通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:30.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不对  我觉得这显得更可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:33.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:35.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在通往这个藏匿地的道路上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:39.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然已经撤下了能扰乱狼的嗅觉的药
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:42.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是需要多加注意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:43.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,别在外面乱走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:44.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:47.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果到明天中午前我还没回来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:49.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就在米吉多的城市会合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.83,0:13:53.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  你们移动时必须充分警惕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:54.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:56.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:58.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.84,0:14:01.97,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我也趁现在去取点水回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:03.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我也帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:04.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:05.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:07.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.10,0:14:08.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,有话跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:11.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是帕斯卡尔说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:13.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,要你跟瞬好好相处之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:16.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们又没有吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:18.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是这家伙每句话都顶撞别人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:20.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是是  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.28,0:14:23.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那  我去去就回  好好相处哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:25.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:26.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:28.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  你先坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:30.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,别对我下命令  你倒是给我先坐下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:37.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:39.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,给我听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:41.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了别对我下命令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:42.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要离开这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:44.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:46.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想回去对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:47.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:49.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此就帮我一把吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:50.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:53.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算打倒德尔扎因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:55.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,把国王打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.15,0:14:59.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会帮你干这种事呢绝对不帮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:01.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:05.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想回去啊  但我没有干那种事情的打算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.11,0:15:07.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,德尔扎因也朝巴比伦进发了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:11.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,若是那家伙先到达的话  你就不可能回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:15.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说  要在那之前打倒那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:18.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这也太鲁莽了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:19.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我有作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:21.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,作战计划？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:23.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  所以你得协助我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:26.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:28.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那  要怎样做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:31.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,今晩  艾丽西亚睡着之后我们就离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.81,0:15:34.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不带上艾丽西亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:37.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,被她发现的话会有各种麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.61,0:15:39.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:40.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:43.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,欢  欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:45.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪  怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.24,0:15:47.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:48.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙  太不自然了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:50.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,才  才没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:52.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,会败露的  大方一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:53.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:55.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么呢  你们怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:15:57.96,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:15:59.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  艾米里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:01.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,帕斯卡尔不在期间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:03.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还是采集一些蘑菇之类的会比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:04.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,说  说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:07.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是呢  不也一副慌张无措样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:08.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:11.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到底在闹哪一出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:13.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好  去狩猎吧  我出去狩措
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:15.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你也跟过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.93,0:16:18.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,放手用嘴叫我就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:21.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的要是败露的话全都是你错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:24.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这句话我原封不动还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:33.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.91,0:16:37.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你这算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:41.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这么做比较有气势  看起来也很强  不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.13,0:16:44.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙  用得越来越熟练了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:55.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你从对面把猎物逼过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:58.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里埋伏  确实地给它致命一击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:16:59.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:00.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:02.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想说你那么轻松真舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:06.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  最后结果它才是最艰难的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:08.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才说你是狩措的门外汉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:09.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.20,0:17:10.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:30.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,它来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:34.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,很好继续这样赶它过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:38.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:44.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:55.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:00.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  我最强吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:02.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.87,0:18:05.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,连我特意让给你点面子你都没注意到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:08.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哈  你刚才摔倒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:09.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你那是在演戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:12.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:14.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  抓到了很厉害的家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:18.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,等下  你怎么能把功劳都揽到自己身上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:20.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.52,0:18:22.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,给它最后一击的可是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:23.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:24.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:25.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:27.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我 才 不 闭 嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.44,0:18:28.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 不要吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:31.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.24,0:18:34.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,又是那野猪火锅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:35.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是ENDORA野猪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:37.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:38.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但明明是猪的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:42.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会是这种令人提不起食欲的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:43.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:45.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我开吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:48.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:50.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,看来只能吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:18:57.47,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,美味得让你哭出来了吗瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.32,0:19:14.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:16.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:25.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,出发了  跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:19:57.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:19:58.70,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:00.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.08,0:20:03.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:05.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是帮手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.54,0:20:07.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,帮手  怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:09.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:25.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,王国的人随意靠近这里可不太好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:27.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,会被杀哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.90,0:20:34.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果明知我们是伊格纳茨还敢踏足这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:36.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那还真是有勇气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:39.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,若非如此  那就纯粹是笨蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:42.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你说的帮手去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.66,0:20:44.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦  还有帮手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:48.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,帮手在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:49.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,敢动一下  就杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:52.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,帮手就是这群人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:57.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你的话真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.84,0:21:13.68,geci,,0,0,0,,兜兜转转   迂迂回回
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:21.77,geci,,0,0,0,,时至今日的种种  成就了今天的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.89,0:21:28.61,geci,,0,0,0,,go my way    go my way
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:48.88,geci,,0,0,0,,世界轮回   将从未见过的未来映照于青空之上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.55,0:21:57.60,geci,,0,0,0,,超越过去超越自我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:22:04.81,geci,,0,0,0,,希望今天能以欣欣笑颜出现在你的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.02,0:22:10.07,geci,,0,0,0,,要聊点什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.11,0:22:18.24,geci,,0,0,0,,夏日的清香纠缠着心灵的悸动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.78,0:22:29.17,geci,,0,0,0,,难以言喻的情感只为传达那一句  喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.68,0:22:43.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,下回  伊格纳茨
